data.title: Call of Duty Store
data.text:
REBIRTH ISLAND

Deploy to Rebirth Island, now under control of the occupying Konni Group as they refit the island for their own nefarious needs. Though the points of interest will be instantly familiar to veteran players, there’s plenty to discover including navigable waterways, retrofitted infrastructure, and the weathered remnants of former occupants. Featuring a variable time of day, map-changing infil strikes, and more, this is a whole new way to play the fan-favorite map.

URZIKSTAN

Drop into Urzikstan, an urban landscape with a familiar feel across 11 major points-of-interest. From the iconic Popov Power Plant in the North all the way through to the Zaravan Suburbs in the South – there's a favorite hot-drop for everyone. Take over the Drivable Train, leverage Horizontal Ziplines to improve movement, and fight your way out of the Gulag. With Contracts and Public Events, this mix of classic and evolving gameplay will have you and the squad dropping in for more.

Compatible with PS5 & PS4

BATTLE PASS BUNDLE BONUS

Unlock new gear and goodies even faster. PlayStation players that purchase a Battle Pass Bundle will get an additional 5 tier skips. That’s a total of 25 tier skips.

COMBAT PACKS

Get a free††† in-game bundle each Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III season. Includes such items as an Operator Skin, Weapon Blueprint, Emblem and much more. Limited time only for PlayStation Plus members.

EXTRA LOADOUTS

Be prepared for any scenario. PlayStation players get an additional 2 loadout slots, ready for customization. Available when Create-A-Class unlocks upon reaching Level 4.

DOUBLE XP POINTS

PlayStation players can look forward to exclusive Monthly Double XP events (24 hr duration), so prepare to boost your rank.

PLAYSTATION PARTY BONUS

Teamwork makes the dream work. PlayStation players that play together in parties receive +25% bonus weapon XP. The bonus still counts when playing with cross-platform teammates.

†††PlayStation Plus Required.

NEW ANTI-CHEAT SYSTEM

RICOCHET Anti-Cheat™ initiative is a multi-faceted approach to combat cheating, featuring new server-side tools which monitor analytics to identify cheating, enhanced investigation processes to stamp out cheaters, updates to strengthen account security, and more. RICOCHET Anti-Cheat’s backend anti-cheat security features is live for Call of Duty®: Modern Warfare® III, Call of Duty®: Modern Warfare® II, Call of Duty®: Vanguard, and Call of Duty®: Warzone™.

Call of Duty: Modern Warfare III, Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II, Call of Duty: Warzone, and Call of Duty: Vanguard on PC also utilizes a new PC kernel-level driver, developed internally for the Call of Duty franchise as part of the RICOCHET Anti-Cheat initiative. The driver is currently live in Modern Warfare III, Modern Warfare II, Vanguard, and Warzone, globally.

HOW IT WORKS

RICOCHET Anti-Cheat brings a broad enhancement to the security to Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II, Call of Duty: Vanguard, and Call of Duty: Warzone. As part of this multi-faceted anti-cheat security initiative is a new kernel-level driver on PC, currently live for Modern Warfare III, Modern Warfare II, Vanguard, and Warzone. The new initiative allows for rapid iteration to combat a sophisticated and evolving problem.
